{"tid":1375462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦膠箱護國徽　警員門外巡邏","createTime":"2019-07-28T05:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T07:33:56.000Z","uid":35790,"like":130,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"c31807221403fdb6de7330b147cf8b91224b6b70","tid":1375462,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:19:10.000Z","msg":"修例風波：中聯辦膠箱護國徽　警員門外巡邏 <br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》風波引起的衝突持續，昨日(27日)元朗發生多番衝突後，今日(28日)將有市民發起中上環遊行，雖然遊行申請未獲警方批出不反對通知書，但為嚴防受到衝擊，中聯辦亦加強布防，外圍早已架起多個水馬。中午時分，中聯辦大樓上次遭示威者以漆彈擲污的國徽，已安裝上透明膠箱保護，門外更有多名警員巡邏。 <br />\n<br />\n而昨晚在干諾道西和德輔道西東西行行人路，有工人於地磚塗抹膠水，疑為防止有人掘磚。今日清晨7時許，可見有多名警員於門外把守。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190728/mobile/bkn-20190728020659370-0728_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190728%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190728020659370-0728_00822_001.html&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=26df5ab1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190728/mobile/bkn-20190728020659370-0728_00822_001.html</a>&lt;圖&gt;"},{"pid":"75e92d43ef49f7a61a909ba1fbc27ec54a565a64","tid":1375462,"uid":246026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"請和理非同埋鍵戰嘅你入嚟望下<br />\n[急] [ 突發] 聽日會出席嘅和理非同勇武入一入嚟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373809</a>"},{"pid":"e10ca573b60d611a7792da3470e9c7875638d6b1","tid":1375462,"uid":65530,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:19:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aee77dcfe6a1152da258869a570c9d6874d9479","tid":1375462,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dafe7b6a79e8c576e9e228ee0f58d2cdcdc01ad","tid":1375462,"uid":3549,"like":188,"dislike":1,"score":187,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:21:17.000Z","msg":"痴個大既強國